name: Insaerndel

aspects.trouble: Caught Between Thalmor and Thieves Guild

notes: Insaerndel is a Thieves Guild operative working to establish a foothold in Whiterun during the Battle of Whiterun. Has successfully negotiated with House Battle-Born and neutralized the Thalmor intelligence node in the city.
